{
  "texts": [
    "Zhang et al (2022b) propose a neural hierarchical topic model to discover hierarchical topics from documents.",
    "Then they generate keyphrases under the hierarchical topic guidance.",
    "Similar to early work (Wang and Blei 2011), NTMs can cooperate with recommendation systems.",
    "Esmaeili et al (2019) combines a NTM with a recommender system for reviews through a structured auto-encoder.",
    "Xie et al (2021) use a graph NTM for citation recommendation."
  ]
}